{
  "texts": [
    "• Structural outlines: Students may use AI to create structured outlines of their work.",
    "• Research assistance: AI may be used to suggest topics, areas of interest, or sources (using an Internet-connected model) that might be useful for a student's research.",
    "At Level 3, students are permitted to employ generative AI for refining, editing, and enhancing the language or content of their original work.",
    "This may be particularly beneficial for non-native English speakers or those who struggle with language fluency.",
    "In a multimodal approach to assessment, GenAI tools might be permitted to support the editing of images or videos, but not for creating entirely new pieces."
  ]
}